00:01:55.920 --> 00:02:02.310
It’s within such a list of hidden pleasures
that we find the joy of reading in bed together.

00:02:02.310 --> 00:02:08.009
It represents in its own way a major psychological
skill. There’s not really anyone else we

00:02:08.009 --> 00:02:13.590
could do this with. If the world were fairer,
we would seek partners not just who can perform

00:02:13.590 --> 00:02:20.170
spectacular sexual antics and look hot in
a bar, but also those with whom we could one

00:02:20.170 --> 00:02:27.890
day turn pages in silence. To read together
is symbolic of being able to share our true

00:02:27.890 --> 00:02:33.720
selves without shame, embarrassment or the
need to perform. We are, as we lie in bed

00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:41.000
together, as we so seldom are in the rest
of life, simply accepted. Long-term relationships

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:48.250
are, inevitably, deeply complicated enterprises.
Two ambitious, independent authentic people

00:02:48.250 --> 00:02:54.520
cannot hope to join their lives together without
a huge amount of friction and pain. We tend

00:02:54.520 --> 00:03:00.540
to be so much aware of the troubles, we sometimes
take the peaceable moments for granted, failing

00:03:00.540 --> 00:03:06.840
to appreciate their underlying achievement.
It may lack glamour, but being able to read

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:14.010
in bed together with someone is a major milestone;
and a sign of deep affection. We may be doing

00:03:14.010 --> 00:03:16.800
better than we think.

